OL,3,CMan charged with breaching restraining
OL,4,Corder against contact with PCC
OL,6,FA 59-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith breaching a restraining order
OL,8,Fprohibiting contact with Hampshire and
OL,9,FIsle of Wight Police and Crime
OL,10,FCommissioner Donna Jones.
OL,12,FRobert Hood, of Kingsley Road, in
OL,13,FSouthsea, is set to appear at
OL,14,FPortsmouth Magistrates' Court in
OL,15,Frelation to the offence, a second
OL,16,Foffence of harassment without violence
OL,17,Fagainst a second person.
