OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777050358
OL,3,CMan charged with breaching restraining
OL,4,Corder against contact with PCC
OL,6,FA Hampshire Constabulary spokesman
OL,7,Fsaid: "We can confirm that 59-year-old
OL,8,FRobert Hood of Kingsley Road in
OL,9,FSouthsea has been charged with one
OL,10,Foffence of breach of a restraining
OL,11,Forder against Police and Crime
OL,12,FCommissioner Donna Jones and
OL,13,Fharassment without violence against a
OL,14,Fsecond victim.
OL,16,F"He has been remanded to appear at
OL,17,FPortsmouth Magistrates' Court on
OL,18,FFriday 24 April.
OL,26,@oD@GOUxD@AOU
