CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777050358
OL,3,CMan charged with breaching restraining
OL,4,Corder against contact with PCC
OL,6,F"The charges follow incidents that
OL,7,Ftook place between 23 March and 22
OL,8,FApril."
OL,10,FMs Jones became the youngest serving
OL,11,Fmember of the judiciary when she
OL,12,Fbecame a magistrate in 2005 and has
OL,13,Falso served as Conservative leader of
OL,14,FPortsmouth City Council before being
OL,15,Felected to the PCC role in 2021.
OL,17,FShe is also chairwoman of the
OL,18,FAssociation of Police and Crime
OL,19,FCommissioners (APCC).
